OL,3,CPlymouth man 'waited nine hours in the
OL,4,Cback of an ambulance' with chest pains
OL,6,FA Plymouth man has described waiting
OL,7,Ffour hours for an ambulance and
OL,8,Fanother nine hours outside hospital
OL,9,Fbefore finally being given a bed.
OL,11,FGary Bowman, who lives on the tenth
OL,12,Ffloor of a tower block, suffered chest
OL,13,Fpains at his home in West Park last
OL,14,Fweekend and called 111, who sent
OL,15,Fparamedics.
OL,17,F"As soon as they got me to Derriford
OL,18,Fthey took me in, initially for an ECG,
OL,19,Fbloods, a chest X-ray.
