OL,3,CPlymouth man 'waited nine hours in the
OL,4,Cback of an ambulance' with chest pains
OL,6,F"Then I was put back in the back of
OL,7,Fthe ambulance, and I was there until
OL,8,F8.30am the following morning, (which)
OL,9,Fstopped two paramedics and their
OL,10,Fambulance going out, attending other
OL,11,Femergencies."
OL,13,FGary was eventually given a bed, and
OL,14,Fis thankfully back home and on the
OL,15,Fmend. But he's just one example of a
OL,16,Fcrisis which is almost becoming
OL,17,Fnormality.
