OL,4,Cback of an ambulance' with chest pains
OL,6,F"I told my family if you ever need to
OL,7,Fgo to A&E, I don't think I'd phone
OL,8,F999. You don't want to be stuck in the
OL,9,Fback of an ambulance."
OL,11,FEarlier this week University Plymouth
OL,12,FHospitals Trust announced yet another
OL,13,Fcritical incident, the fifth one this
OL,14,Fyear.
OL,16,FThis one was triggered by IT problems,
OL,17,Fwhich affected key clinical systems
OL,18,Fwithin the hospital, making it harder
OL,19,Fto process patients and causing even
OL,20,Flonger backlogs than usual.
