OL,6,FThe critical incident .
OL,8,FJames Merrell, from the Royal College
OL,9,Fof Nursing, said: "Our members are
OL,10,Fstill reporting that they are under
OL,11,Fconstant pressure to do more for less,
OL,12,Fand the impact on them and their
OL,13,Fwellbeing is huge. So it's no wonder
OL,14,Fwhy nursing staff are leaving the
OL,15,Fprofession."
