OL,6,FPoliticians on both sides are agreed
OL,7,Fthat something needs to be done, and
OL,8,Fhealthcare is sure to be a key issue
OL,9,Fwhen it comes the general election.
OL,10,FLuke Pollard, Labour MP for Plymouth
OL,11,FSutton and Devonport, said: "The
OL,12,Fcrisis is deepening in our NHS, and
OL,13,Fthere doesn't seem to be a clear plan
OL,14,Ffrom ministers as to how they're going
OL,15,Fto get their out of this situation.
