OL,3,CPlymouth man 'waited nine hours in the
OL,4,Cback of an ambulance' with chest pains
OL,6,F"It's not just about the hospital,
OL,7,Fit's about the lack of primary care
OL,8,FGPs, it's about social care falling
OL,9,Fover. It's a whole system problem and
OL,10,Fit's getting worse. We need a clear
OL,11,Fplan from government as to how are we
OL,12,Fgoing to fix it."
OL,14,FRebecca Smith, Conservative
OL,15,FParliamentary candidate for South West
OL,16,FDevon, said: "It's clearly an issue
OL,17,Fwhen the hospital is under pressure
OL,18,Flike this.
