OL,6,F"However, having met with them
OL,7,Frecently, I know that they're doing an
OL,8,Fincredible amount of work supported by
OL,9,Fthe NHS to ensure that these critical
OL,10,Fincidences become a thing of the past.
OL,12,F"The most exciting thing is the new,
OL,13,Furgent and emergency care treatment
OL,14,Fcentre that is being built at
OL,15,FDerriford that is going to free up the
OL,16,Fmost emergency needs and enable a lot
OL,17,Fof those who just need to walk in and
OL,18,Fget same day emergency treatment to
OL,19,Fhave that done."
