OL,6,FA spokesperson for University
OL,7,FHospitals Plymouth NHS Trust said:
OL,8,F"This week we have seen a high-level
OL,9,Fof operational pressure on our
OL,10,Fservices and, alongside experiencing
OL,11,FIT issues, we declared a Business
OL,12,FContinuity Incident and Critical
OL,13,FIncident.
OL,15,F"As the Major Trauma Centre for the
OL,16,Fsouthwest peninsula, we receive some
OL,17,Fof the most acutely unwell patients by
OL,18,Fair and road ambulance.
