OL,6,F"We prioritise patients in order of
OL,7,Fclinical need, however we understand
OL,8,Fpatients and their families will be
OL,9,Fconcerned about long waits in
OL,10,Fambulances and for access to some of
OL,11,Four services.
OL,13,F"We apologise to patients who
OL,14,Fexperience delays to their care, or
OL,15,Fpostponements of planned surgeries.
OL,16,FOur staff are working really hard to
OL,17,Fget patients to the right place, at
OL,18,Fthe right time."
